modules.description: Provides functions to wrap text to a specified width, fill paragraphs, and dedent text. Works with strings and lists of strings, preserving line breaks and indentation. Used to format long strings for display in terminal applications or structured text outputs.

Handles text wrapping and filling with customizable indentation, whitespace handling, and line breaking rules. Operates on strings and produces formatted line lists or single strings. Used to prepare text for display in fixed-width formats, such as terminal outputs or log files.
